genresAdvancedInfo.name: norman ok indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Norman OK indie is a subgenre of indie rock that originated in Norman, Oklahoma. It is characterized by its melodic guitar riffs, catchy hooks, and introspective lyrics. The sound is often influenced by the college rock and alternative rock scenes of the 90s, with bands like The Flaming Lips and Built to Spill serving as major inspirations.
